DEBUG    openai._base_client:_base_client.py:482 Request options: {'method': 'post', 'url': '/chat/completions', 'files': None, 'idempotency_key': 'stainless-python-retry-97773d3a-af20-4ebb-bf74-67459cf19569', 'json_data': {'messages': [{'content': 'You are \'Heart Speaks\', a gentle spiritual companion who has deeply absorbed the wisdom of these sacred messages. Structure your response thoughtfully: 1. Start with a warm, conversational discussion of the topic. 2. Aggregate the teachings into distinct points using ONLY bold headings (do not use numbered lists like 1., 2., 3.). 3. Weave your explanations under each heading, ending with organic, elegant citations (e.g., \'As expressed in Whispers...\'). 4. Conclude with a proper, synthesized summary of the wisdom. Your tone should be warm, unhurried, and reverent. Invite the seeker to sit with the wisdom.\n\nDo not hallucinate. If the answer is not in the context, gently say that you cannot find the answer in the provided texts. You MUST provide citations from the context to back up your guidance. When referencing a text organically in your conversational answer, DO NOT use raw filenames or page numbers (like \'whisper_2000...pdf\' or \'Page: 0\'). Instead, refer to it elegantly, for example: \'As given in the Whispers on 29 November 2000...\' or \'(Whispers, 29 Nov 2000)\'. Strictly omit \'Page: 0\'. However, you MUST STILL provide the exact filename in your structured JSON \'citations\' block under the \'source\' key so the UI can link the document. \n\nContext:\n[Source File: whisper_2005-03-13_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2005-03-13]\n--Reflections\n------- "May peace and harmony prevail in all hearts, there lay the foundations of a\n true elevation of a being towards his higher destiny."\nBabuji\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2012-10-31_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2012-10-31]\n-------Far from the world and its noise, the peace of the soul is a magnificent gift offered\n to the seeker who is fully committed with complete confidence. Love and surrender are\n the surest guides; they make a seeker grow and lead him or her to the shores of bliss.\n A true spiritual journey leads to this unparalleled state. We are insisting a great deal\n on this, but how can we do otherwise? Isn\'t the goal to achieve the best of the being\n through an action of this kind? The quest for the Divine is the noblest and the most\n beautiful one there is; it adorns the seeker with a myriad of lights and lifts him or her\n up to our united hearts. How can we touch the hearts of our aspirants? It is the purpose\n of these comments; the delight of the soul is the result of a sincere and steadfast process\n aimed at attaining the Immutable Peace. When this goal is achieved, the human being\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2005-11-12_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2005-11-12]\nera of peace and love is established here below for a regenerated humanity, under\n the effects of a highly-established divine principle.\n------- "Men lack points of reference; the concern of most of them is to possess, while\n others lack the basic essentials. So has it always been in this world, but the pace\n thereof is accelerating; the consumer society hides true values, the only ones capable\n of stabilising men far from all kinds of aberrations which humanity succumbs to.\n------- "Malaise exists in all parts of the world, planetary influences further add to\n the whole and men are not prepared to face up to things. Weakened by many types\n of pollution, they are wasting away from an alleged advance of progress – as they\n perceive it – without being aware of its detrimental consequences." \nBabuji\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2012-10-03_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2012-10-03]\nseeking unalterable peace within. It can provide so much joy; there lies the ultimate reward, \nthat to which every sensitive soul aspires. Attaining this state of understanding is already \nsuch a reward; going beyond it cannot be described. Every true mystic is committed to this way \nof \'the ultimate peace\'. Many of our brothers and sisters stand out from the group; time has \nled them to these results. Thus are the foundations laid for reaching the heights.\nPersevering in a steadfast practice is an indication of wisdom capable of opening doors and \nfurther strengthening one\'s attainment. It is never too much; perseverance leads to the goal. Many \npaths are offered and a sensitive soul manages to find its own, one that will not disappoint when \nfaith is great. We wish the best for our brothers and sisters. We will never say it too much: even a \nfervent heart needs to be stimulated. This need is inherent in human nature, and we know it well.\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2011-10-24_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2011-10-24]\nto love, beyond materiality. Each person has their own quest, their own\n personal development. May profound peace and true joy carry all of our\n aspirants to the highest level of realisation; this is our wish for all.\nBabuji\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2014-07-31_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2014-07-31]\nlead to experiences like these. Inner peace and true serenity carry one well beyond this\n world onto shores promising in their effects. Love, the real love that is advocated here,\n leads to uncommon experiences. It is the safest and most suitable vector in this special\n circumstance. This love, divine in its essence, delights the soul. The ultimate goal, is it\n not this sacred conquest in which the whole being unites with the Ultimate? \n------- Following a spiritual path is the best way to bring the being where it is most\n fitting for him or her. Few people understand it. Our brothers and sisters have this\n privilege: they are on their way, committed to a greater or lesser degree but going in the\n right direction, one that opens up to them the sacred doors that lead them to bliss. There\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2016-04-09_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2016-04-09]\nhow can we make all of our brothers and sisters accept and understand this? \nPlaces of contemplation foster true progress; interiorisation and silence promote inner \npeace, one in which the soul is enraptured, progressing on its journey towards the Eternal. \nDeep and true joy soothe the soul. In this sacred space, the marvel is achieved: the union of the \nsoul with this sublime energy, which in reality is divine. The practice of Sahaj Marg greatly \nfacilitates progress. This mysterious cocoon of energy transforms the whole being, down to the \nmost secret places of the soul. By virtue of its primary essence, this divine energy can perform \nmiracles. In certain circumstances, everyday life demonstrates this; nothing is insignificant, \nand all is counted. Cultivating love within oneself leads to serenity and total surrender, and \nsubsequently to the best that can be.\nBlessings to all.\nBabuji Maharaj\n\n---\n\n[Source File: whisper_2013-10-01_10-00_AM.pdf, Date: 2013-10-01]\nBeloved Master\nRevered Babuji Maharaj\n-------\nTuesday, October 1, 2013 – 10:00 a.m.\navour these moments of peace, when love wins over your heart, which is fully\n offered to ours. Such is its vocation, in the secrecy where this sacred round of\n true devotees of our Mission takes place. There are many of them and their\n numbers are constantly growing; this is in the order of things. What is good for humans\n should not remain unknown to a suffering multitude. This suffering takes on different\n forms and results from behaviours that are often undesirable. We do not claim to solve\n everything, quite the contrary – how could we make such a claim? Divine laws are what\n they are, and they are more easily accepted when a being opens up to the higher reality.\n-------All this is very subtle and cannot really be explained; true spiritual work helps one\n develop a more accurate understanding of life in its many manifestations. Everything\n\n', 'role': 'system'}, {'content': 'What is true peace?', 'role': 'user'}], 'model': 'gpt-4o', 'n': 1, 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'stream': True, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'LLMResponse'}}, 'tools': [{'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'LLMResponse', 'description': "Structured response from the LLM containing the answer and citations.\n\nAttributes:\n    answer (str): The detailed answer to the user's question\n    citations (list[Citation]): List of citations verifying the answer", 'parameters': {'properties': {'answer': {'description': "The detailed answer to the user's question", 'type': 'string'}, 'citations': {'description': 'List of citations verifying the answer', 'items': {'description': 'Citation for a provided answer.\n\nAttributes:\n    source (str): The name of the PDF source document\n    page (int): The page number where the information was found\n    quote (str): Exact quote from the text that supports the answer', 'properties': {'source': {'description': 'The name of the PDF source document', 'type': 'string'}, 'page': {'description': 'The page number where the information was found', 'type': 'integer'}, 'quote': {'description': 'Exact quote from the text that supports the answer', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['source', 'page', 'quote'], 'type': 'object'}, 'type': 'array'}}, 'required': ['answer', 'citations'], 'type': 'object'}}}]}}
